title: Malcolm Douglas - Australia - Canoes In The Kimberley [1982]
description: Malcolm Douglas - 4x06 - Canoes In The Kimberley - 1982 Adventure / Travel / Documentary https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malcolm_Douglas_(documentary_maker) In this classic adventure Malcolm travels with his Aboriginal companions in two Canadian canoes down the Charnley River gorge in the Kimberley. They are the first people to traverse this spectacular river chasm. On reaching the sea they fit out-riggers to the big canoes to complete the journey down the rugged coast to Derby.
